featured.text: Under the _____ of newly elected president Barack Obama, the US is expected to turn a new page in politics and economy.

definition.zh_def: 巴拉克（Barack）是一個常見的男性名字，源自阿拉伯語，意為「祝福」。
definition.en_def: Barack is a common male name of Arabic origin meaning 'blessed'.
definition.example: Barack Obama was the 44th President of the United States.
